(335, 12, 'Is it raining? No.', 'ฝนตกไหมคะ ไม่ตกค่ะ', 'Fŏhn dtòk mái khá? Mâi dtòk khâ', 'rain - fall - or not - polite particle? not - fall - polite particle', '', 'f12_2'),
(336, 12, 'Is it tasty? Yes.', 'อร่อยไหมคะ อร่อยค่ะ', 'À-ròy mái khá? À-ròy khâ', 'tasty - or not - polite particle? tasty - polite particle', '', 'f12_3'),
(337, 12, 'Was it expensive? No.', 'แพงไหมคะ ไม่แพงค่ะ', 'Phaaeng mái khá? Mâi phaaeng khâ', 'expensive - or not - polite particle? not - expensive - polite particle', '', 'f12_4'),
(338, 12, 'You''re going shopping, right? Yes.', 'คุณกำลังจะไปซื้อของใช่ไหมคะ ใช่ค่ะ', 'Khun gamlang-jà bpai séu kăwng châi mái khá? Châi khâ', 'you - about to - go - buy - stuff - yes - or no - polite particle? yes - polite particle', 'We use ''châi mái'' when there is an assumption which needs confirmation. ', 'f12_5'),
(339, 12, 'Your mother is Thai, right? No.', 'แม่เป็นคนไทยใช่ไหมคะ ไม่ใช่ค่ะ', 'Mâe bpen khon Thai châi mái khá? Mâi-châi khâ', 'mother - is - person - Thai - yes - or no - polite particle? no - polite particle', '', 'f12_6'),
(340, 12, 'He''s your boyfriend, isn''t he? No!', 'เขาเป็นแฟนคุณไม่ใช่หรอคะ ไม่ใช่ค่ะ!', 'Khăo bpen faen khun mâi-châi răw khá? Mâi-châi khâ', 'he - is - boyfriend - you - no - question word - polite particle? no - polite particle', 'The expression ''mâi châi răw'' is similar to ''châi mái''.', 'f12_7'),
(341, 12, 'You didn''t tell him, did you? Yes (I did).', 'คุณไม่ได้บอกเขาใช่ไหมคะ ฉันบอกแล้วค่ะ', 'Khun mâi dâi bòrk khăo châi mái khá? Chăn bòrk láew khâ', 'you - not - did - tell - him - yes - or no - polite particle? I - tell - past action marker - polite particle', '', 'f12_8'),
(342, 12, 'Are you going or not? Yes.', 'คุณจะไปหรือเปล่า ไปค่ะ', 'Khun jà bpai rĕuu bplàao? Bpai khâ', 'you - future marker - go - or - not? go - polite particle', 'The term ''rĕuuu bplàao'' expects a straight answer.', 'f12_9'),
(343, 12, 'Is that enough? No.', 'พอแล้วหรือยังคะ ยังค่ะ', 'Phaaw láew rĕuu yang khá? Yang khâ', 'enough - already - or - not yet - polite particle? not yet - polite particle', 'The term ''láew rĕuu yang'' means something like ''already or not yet?''. ''Láew'' is often omitted.', 'f12_10'),
(344, 12, 'Has your older sister come home yet? Yes.', 'พี่สาวคุณมาถึงบ้านหรือยังคะ ถึงแล้วค่ะ', 'Phîi săo khun maa thĕung bâan (láew) rĕuu yang khá? Thĕung láew khâ', 'older sibling - girl - you - come - arrive - home - (already) - or - not yet - polite particle? arrive - already - polite particle', '', 'f12_11'),
(345, 12, 'What''s the time?', 'กี่โมงแล้วคะ', 'Gìi mohng láew khá?', 'how many - hour - already - polite particle', '', 'f12_12'),
(346, 12, 'What''s this?', 'อันนี้คืออะไรคะ', 'An níi kheu à-rai khá?', 'item - this - is - what - polite particle?', '', 'f12_13'),
(347, 12, 'What''s his name?', 'เขาชื่ออะไรคะ', 'Khăo chêu à-rai khá?', 'he - called - what - polite particle', '', 'f12_14'),
(348, 12, 'Who am I speaking with? (On the phone)', 'ฉันกำลังพูดอยู่กับใครคะ', 'Chăn gamlang phôot yùu gùp krai khá?', 'I - currently - speak - currently - with - who - polite particle?', '', 'f12_15'),
(349, 12, 'Whose is this? It''s mine.', 'นี้ของใครคะ ของฉันค่ะ', 'Níi kăwng krai khá? Kăwng chăn khâ', 'this - belonging to - who - polite particle? belonging to - me - polite particle', '', 'f12_16'),
(350, 12, 'Which one do you want?', 'คุณอยากได้อันไหนคะ', 'Khun yàak dâi an năi khá?', 'you - want - receive - piece - which - polite particle?', 'The word ''dâi'' has various uses. In this case it means ''get'' or ''receive''.', 'f12_17'),
(351, 12, 'Where is the nearest sky train station?', 'สถานีรถไฟฟ้าไหนที่ใกล้ที่สุดคะ', 'Sà-thăa-nii rót fai fáa năi thîi glâi thîi-sùt khá? ', 'station - vehicle - fire - sky - which - that - near - most - polite particle?', '', 'f12_18'),
(352, 12, 'Where were you born?', 'คุณเกิดที่ไหนคะ', 'Khun gèrt thîi năi khá?', 'you - born - place - which - polite particle', '', 'f12_19'),
