(406, 15, 'Have you finished your homework yet? Yes.', 'การบ้านเสร็จหรือยังคะ เสร็จแล้วค่ะ', 'Gaan bâan sèt (láew) rĕuu yang khá? Sèt láew khâ', 'task - home - finish - (already) - or - not yet - polite particle? finish - already - polite particle', '', 'f15_15'),
(407, 15, 'Has father come home yet? Not yet.', 'พ่อกลับมาบ้านหรือยังคะ ยังค่ะ', 'Phâaw glàp maa bâan rĕuu yang khá? Yang khâ', 'father - return - come - home - or - not yet - polite particle? not yet - polite particle', '', 'f15_16'),
(408, 15, 'Have you been to the doctor already? Yes.', 'ไปหาหมอมาหรือยังคะ ไปมาแล้วค่ะ', 'Bpai hăa mŏr maa rĕuu yang khá? Bpai maa láew khâ', 'go - visit - doctor - come back - or - not yet - polite particle? go - come back - already - polite particle', 'Using ''bpai'' and ''maa'' together in a sentence can imply a trip which has finished.', 'f15_17'),
(409, 15, 'Have you eaten yet? Yes.', 'ทานข้าวหรือยังคะ ทานแล้วค่ะ', 'Thaan khâao rĕuu yang khâ? Than láew khâ', 'eat - rice - (or) - not yet - polite particle? eat - already', '', 'f15_18'),
(410, 15, 'It''s still raining.', 'ฝนยังตกอยู่เลยค่ะ', 'Fŏhn yang dtòk yùu leuuy khâ', 'rain - still - fall - currently - exclamation - polite particle', '', 'f15_19'),
(411, 15, 'He''s still here.', 'เขายังอยู่ที่นี่ค่ะ', 'Khăo yang yùu thîi-nîi ná khâ', 'he - still - situated - here - softening particle - polite particle', '', 'f15_20'),
(412, 15, 'Waan is in a meeting now.', 'หวานกำลังประชุมอยู่ค่ะ', 'Wăan gamlang bprà-choom yùu khâ', 'Waan - currently - meeting - currently - polite particle', 'The construction ''gamlang .... yùu'' is used to talk about something that is currently happening or was happening. Either ''gamlang'' or yùu'' may be dropped.', 'f15_21'),
(413, 15, 'Older sister is watching TV.', 'พี่สาวกำลังดูทีวีอยู่ค่ะ', 'Phîi săo gamlang doo tee-wee yùu khâ', 'older sibling - girl - currently - watch - tv - currently - polite particle', '', 'f15_22'),
(414, 15, 'The dog is sleeping.', 'หมากำลังนอนอยู่ค่ะ', 'Măa gamlang norn yùu khâ', 'dog - currently - sleep - currently - polite particle', '', 'f15_23'),
(415, 15, 'He is waiting for the bus.', 'เขากำลังรอรถเมล์อยู่ค่ะ', 'Khăo gamlang raaw rót-maeh yùu khâ', 'he - currently - wait - bus - currently - polite particle', '', 'f15_24'),
(416, 15, 'We just returned from Japan.', 'เราเพิ่งกลับจากญี่ปุ่นมาค่ะ', 'Rao phêerng glàp jàak Yîi-bpun maa khâ', 'we - just - return - from - Japan - come - polite particle', 'The word ''phêerng'' can be used to indicate that something just happened.', 'f15_25'),
(417, 15, 'I only just found out.', 'ฉันเพิ่งรู้ค่ะ', 'Chăn phêerng róo khâ', 'I - recently - know - polite particle', '', 'f15_26'),
(418, 15, 'We used to go to the temple every week.', 'เราเคยไปวัดทุกอาทิตย์ค่ะ', 'Rao ker-ee bpai wát thúk aa-thít khâ', 'we - used to - go - temple - every - week - polite particle', 'The word ''ker-ee'' has two uses. It can be used to talk about whether something has ever happened or not, and to talk about habitual actions in the past.', 'f15_27'),
(419, 15, 'I''ve already seen it. (the movie)', 'ฉันเคยดูแล้วค่ะ', 'Chăn ker-ee doo láew khâ', 'I - already - watch - past action marker - polite particle', '', 'f15_28'),
